8-11-29T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"冬天出手有原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ea364996f0eeedcf141b22dbe9a47f0242c044","tid":921041,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc2b69ad57d4092e10a653b7fae4709888b6f45f","tid":921041,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51c8c965ed016e30dd56cb5e0827add9d6a9d61b","tid":921041,"uid":121146,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"35e435e45ddc4730c2172c41b21b591a9ad709cc","tid":921041,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"歐洲聯軍去左邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:50:56.000Z","msg":"歐盟：冬天喇  俄佬唔供煤氣點算  細聲d  聽唔到  睇唔到  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"冬天出手有原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"歐洲北約一直都只係當你烏克蘭係緩衝區。北約本身已經鎖咗你波羅的海港口，俄羅斯基本上得返黑海有少少話事權，如果北約俾埋烏克蘭加入，鎖埋俄羅斯嘅黑海艦隊，就等於逼狗入窮巷。歐盟更加唔駛講啦，俾你入咪只會拖死埋歐盟經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總括而言，烏克蘭近排咁想修憲以求加入北約，變相觸動到普京神經，咪求其搵幾隻支援東烏克蘭嘅船嚟祭旗囉，講就講到好撚大，但政治現實係，只要一日俄羅斯唔全面佔領烏克蘭，令到歐盟同俄羅斯之間嘅緩衝區消失，北約掂呢個燙手山芋嘅機會微乎其微，而普京亦冇咁蠢直接挑你北約機。"},{"pid":"402496606eff14b530d24e154c5020b04a64f2af","tid":921041,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b719ac3281db20c0c4fefe791b61520fb062608","tid":921041,"uid":190540,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:28:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"如果香港是獨立國家, 即刻送二千億比烏克蘭, 比佢地重建海軍<br />\n<br />\n對付俄佬/中共呢D邪惡國家, 真係人人有責"},{"pid":"514ec297b601d6c6a90f297d7e31c468aa0d7eb4","tid":921041,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep